com.tomeraberbach.mano.assembly

Class Instruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomeraberbach.mano.assembly.Instruction

  • public class Instruction
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing an instruction for Mano's computer as detailed in:
    Computer System Architecture, 3rd edition
    By M. Morris Mano
    Published by Prentice-Hall, c 1993
    Chapter 5, pp 123-172.
